[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rack</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 6 ====
HEADWORD: Rack
<hw>Rack</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Racked</conjf> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧kt)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Racking</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[See <er>Rack</er> that which
